# Scoped to release-sensitive paths only — NOT a `*` catch-all, which would
# require code-owner review on every PR. Pairs with branch protection
# "Require review from Code Owners" + "Required approvals = 0": only PRs that
# touch these paths need the owner's review; everything else can auto-merge.
#
# The workflows are gated so the release/versioning machinery can't change
# unreviewed; CODEOWNERS is self-gated for the same reason.
/.github/workflows/   @degory
/.github/CODEOWNERS   @degory
